  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Both http and ws in same folder sharing the database
   how to start both the server -> using concurrently --> "dev": "concurrently \"nodemon wsIndex.js\" \"nodemon httpIndex.js\""  
   or if want to run seprately
    make two different terminal instances
      run node/nodemon httpIndex.js in first instance
      run node/nodemon wsIndex.js in second instance
    - if nodemon is not present globally can use (npx nodemon httpIndex.js)
    - or can install nodemon globally by ( npm i -g nodemon )

